Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Fujisaki Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'm going to the production office \Nfor the Tokimeki Memorial anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to visit the production company, Studio Pierrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:34.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,Studio Pierrot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:36.40,Sign,,0,0,0,,Digital Animation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Studio Pierrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Scriptwriter, Kuroda-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,director, Kamegaki-san and character designer, \NMotohashi-san are having a brainstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask some questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:16.51,Sign,,0,0,0,,Scriptwriter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,Yosuke Kuroda
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:26.73,Sign,,0,0,0,,Scriptwriter Yosuke Kuroda:\NTrigun / Battle Athletess Daiundoukai / Android Ana Maico 2010 / Tenchi Muyou! / Mahou Shoujo Pretty Sammy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us the difference\Nbetween the game and OVA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I tried to combine the\Ngame's originality with animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,even though similar pictures and characters are used, a game and a film are two different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I drew a line in terms of how close it'd be to the game
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,without losing the excitement of film. \NI hope everyone likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:01.49,Sign,,0,0,0,,What's there to see in Tokimeki Memorial OVA?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two parts. In the first half...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to describe the moment when...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the character's feelings turn\Ninto love, in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In the last half, I focused on the process, \Nin which she confesses her feelings to the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than making a mess,\NI was hoping to describe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the story in a slow, normal\Ntransition of a girl's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,until her confession, \Nafter consultation with Konami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,Director
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:46.09,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hajime Kamegaki
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:52.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,Director Hajime Kamegaki: \NFushigi Yuugi / Ganbarist! Shun / Fushigi Yuugi Part 2 / B't X NEO / Sotsugyou M / Shonen Sunday Commercial
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:57.41,Sign,,0,0,0,,Have you ever played the game, Tokimeki Memorial?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't yet played the game,\Nalthough I've already heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But considering things, I think I was lucky\Nnot to have played it before this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were crazy about it at the time,\NI couldn't have seen it objectively...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And would have made the\Ncharacters to my favorite types...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which would give nasty and\Nstrange impressions to viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,From that point, I'll have fun\Nplaying after I finish this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:49.30,Sign,,0,0,0,,Please tell us about the differences \Nbetween the game and OVA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This depends a lot on everyone's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that this is not\Ndriven by my image alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:04:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In that sense, animation is created by\Nmany people who put their own feelings to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, without being influenced\Nby scenario writer Kuroda-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I would want to find out my favorite girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if some of us get together the drama will develop naturally by expressing our opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:38.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,Who's your favorite character?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was completely unaware but I've been\Nsubjected to lots of information
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and hot stuff about the characters by Kuroda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Apart from Fujisaki, my favorite among the girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,since I like watching baseball,\NI'd like to see a game with Nijino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy if it came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.47,Sign,,0,0,0,,Character Designing Room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:37.78,Sign,,0,0,0,,Character designer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:42.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hideyuki Motohashi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:48.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,Character designer Hideyuki Motohashi: \NFushigi Yuugi / Gambarist! Shun / Fushigi Yuugi Part 2 / Beat X NEO / Sotsugyou M
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:53.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,What is the essence of character design?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Since an animation relies on\Nthe expression in the face...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to give emphasis and\Nadd highlights to the eyes and hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it might be\Ndifferent from the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to appeal to those who\Nsee things visually, in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,by creating characters who can tell\Nstories through their eyes and hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:32.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,Who's your favorite character?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite character, I mean, who I want\Nto draw, is Fujisaki Shiori, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But honestly, Mikihara Megumi-san is my favorite\Nto draw because she has straight hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,While I know every character has\Ntheir own impressive hair style,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,my favorite is Mikihara Megumi-san\Nwith straight hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please send a short message to the fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As I find some new settings\Nto my surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy if everyone is surprised\Nor sad in that sense as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,While watching the video, you'll\Nfind it's like a diary of your play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you remember each scene\Nand the sense of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be happy if you remember\Nyour feelings of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to create scenes which make\Nyou a little shy when you see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that the majority\Nof viewers are men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:08:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to create something which\Nmakes me excited as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and makes me feel upbeat,\Nas if I were in the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take some more time to complete the film, but it is already very exciting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I'll see you in the OVA!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You host, Fujisaki Shiori!
